This is a regression test for GENSYMCID-1308 'G2 list - Bug with list-size'
We check the inability to edit list-size by the absence of 'edit' item in attribute's popup menu

This is a regression test for GENSYMCID-1919 'G2 aborts when concluding the size of G2 List' Root cause of the problem is that one can conclude list-size. So we check that concluding list-size causes an error and that the error message contains the explanation that the attribute is read-only.

RELEASE NOTES This is GENSYMCID-1888, regression test for GENSYMCID-1309 'G2 list - Bug with list-size (bug 2)'
BACKGROUND In many versions of G2 2011, after inserting data into the list and subsequent concluding of g2-list-sequence, the list-size attribute was changed to an incorrect value. Description of the test case in GENSYMCID-1309 was incorrect. The better one is in the testrail case for 1309. We simplified it and accomplished test scenario through procedure, w/o using the UI.
SOLUTION We reproduce simpified testrail case, see the code
TESTING Test fails in G2 2011 STD February 2012 release and passes in HIP2016-09

Those RT-UTIL-* utilities are copy-pasted between many tests. Some of them should be moved into player.kb, others should be moved to some other appropriate place, but we're lacking the time to categorize them properly, invent names for them and move to player.kb
